{"tid":1478991,"cid":21,"subCid":1,"title":"My Little Airport 新歌 《吳小姐》","createTime":"2019-08-16T17:21:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-23T18:01:35.000Z","uid":152262,"like":84,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":35,"replies":[{"pid":"2438f0e6fa6aa3dbd73a789718fa79905eebde71","tid":1478991,"uid":152262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T17:21:22.000Z","msg":"繼《今夜雪糕》後 又黎多一首<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n8月18號一起說go!!!!!<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/B-I2hbclzXc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FB-I2hbclzXc&d=GZKRZRfhFQ75XgsIw24e0ezNZxTp5Qnzjcs1Ew7Eoms%3D&h=e3dcd272\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/B-I2hbclzXc</a>"},{"pid":"d8e6a24c5e34414761b97f5e148b1751bfd3d17e","tid":1478991,"uid":152262,"like":47,"dislike":0,"score":47,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T17:22:05.000Z","msg":"吳小姐畢業之後 <br />\n做咗銀行十幾年 <br />\n最近佢單身 <br />\n罷工嗰日自己一個去彌敦道 <br />\n黃昏嘅時候 <br />\n成條馬路都係黑衫嘅年輕人行嚟行去<br />\n尖沙咀同其他區已經放咗催淚彈<br />\n佢一路行<br />\n一路睇吓live  <br />\n聽下條街啲人講點部署<br />\n<br />\n無幾耐天開始黑 <br />\n行到豉油街<br />\n經過兩間日本嘢<br />\n佢都好想入去食住涼冷氣 <br />\n不過咁好似幫襯咗無罷市嘅食店<br />\n最後佢猶豫咗一陣<br />\n都係喺小販檔買咗兩個桔返示威區 <br />\n坐喺十字街口嘅馬路邊 <br />\n一路食一路有啲涼風<br />\n<br />\n就在她坐下的那個瞬間 <br />\n她竟有前所未有的嘆<br />\n<br />\n食食吓有人問佢要唔要水 <br />\n有人問佢去唔去深水埗警署聲援<br />\n有個女仔指住太子方向 <br />\n話一直行就會到<br />\n吳小姐走咗幾步覺得太遠<br />\n都係搭地鐵<br />\n<br />\n去到現場  <br />\n有人叫佢唔好行咁前<br />\n然後 佢第一次<br />\n親眼見到催淚彈<br />\n佢跟住大家 <br />\n向後褪<br />\n開遮  <br />\n踎低 <br />\n行返前 <br />\n來來回回 <br />\n幾粒催淚彈之後 <br />\n佢有種從未試過嘅感覺<br />\n<br />\n時間突然好慢 <br />\n周圍好靜<br />\n佢覺得呢個瞬間 <br />\n最前線嘅人係自己  <br />\n後面用士巴拿拆緊鐵欄嘅人又係自己<br />\n旁邊鬧緊街坊唔好影相嘅人又係自己 <br />\n遠處坐緊監嘅人又係自己<br />\n<br />\n無幾耐大家話轉場去另一個警署<br />\n吳小姐坐喺紅綠燈下面食咗支煙<br />\n<br />\n就在她坐下的那個瞬間 <br />\n她竟有說不出的感嘆<br />\n<br />\n最後防暴衝出嚟 <br />\n吳小姐狂跑嘅時候  <br />\n竟然跑得快過晒所有嘅人<br />\n佢決定 以後都出嚟"},{"pid":"4df09db7c61774620648f4ae9c6fcc7aeed199f2","tid":1478991,"uid":69221,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T17:22:31.000Z","msg":"好想有人陪我去MLA嘅演唱會<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f74b51a33b36acee78926cf6231dfb3c9cc8cd89","tid":1478991,"uid":152262,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"4df09db7c61774620648f4ae9c6fcc7aeed199f2","tid":1478991,"uid":69221,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T17:22:31.000Z","msg":"好想有人陪我去MLA嘅演唱會<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T18:11:22.000Z","msg":"8月18 上街約人睇將來嘅show!"},{"pid":"4a1e67a62d382f1b0b649ab553239eae90826d1d","tid":1478991,"uid":36673,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T18:13:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28454b624e709e19e20667f9f913f3d8beddd655","tid":1478991,"uid":69221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f74b51a33b36acee78926cf6231dfb3c9cc8cd89","tid":1478991,"uid":152262,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"4df09db7c61774620648f4ae9c6fcc7aeed199f2","tid":1478991,"uid":69221,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T17:22:31.000Z","msg":"好想有人陪我去MLA嘅演唱會<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T18:11:22.000Z","msg":"8月18 上街約人睇將來嘅show!"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T18:13:36.000Z","msg":"手持美國旗相認"},{"pid":"4383540a0f901c696204646877f456cf2f3d6f8c","tid":1478991,"uid":5258,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T18:13:44.000Z","msg":"Pish<br />\nmla<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />又話香港無我嘅事"},{"pid":"97b84b9ee66b96c0d51c6d12994aa6c1d5ceeaad","tid":1478991,"uid":152262,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"28454b624e709e19e20667f9f913f3d8beddd655","tid":1478991,"uid":69221,"like":0,"disli